{"language": "plaintext", "code": "//+------------------------------------------------------------------+
//|  BreakoutNY_v3_DJI30_FP.mq5                                     |
//|  BreakoutNY Strategy — DJI30 (Dow Jones) — FundingPips          |
//|  Timeframe : M5                                                  |
//|  Version   : 3.0                                                 |
//|  Date      : March 2026                                          |
//|                                                                  |
//|  CHANGES FROM v2:                                                |
//|  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────   |
//|  [FIX] Lot calculation: MathRound() instead of MathFloor()      |
//|         MathFloor(0.0170/0.01)*0.01 = 0.01 ✓ (both work now)   |
//|         But MathFloor(0.0250/0.01)*0.01 = 0.02 ✓               |
//|         The real fix is the $100k account making lotsRaw >= 0.01 |
//|  [NEW]  BE_BufferPct = 50% — sweet spot between v1(20%) & v4    |
//|         BE activates when price travels 50% of SL distance       |
//|         Once activated: SL moves to entry (zero risk)            |
//|  [NEW]  RiskAmountUSD = 1000 (1% of $100k simulated account)    |
//|         Dynamic lots now work: range 0.01–0.02 across SL sizes  |
//|  [NEW]  Separate BE state from TP1/TP2 state (cleaner logic)    |
//|  [NEW]  OnInit prints lot calculation test for verification      |
//|                                                                  |
//|  TRADE MANAGEMENT LOGIC (v3):                                    |
//|    Entry   → SL at entry ± slDist (LOCKED until BE activates)   |
//|    BE zone → When price reaches entry ± slDist × 50%:           |
//|              SL moves to entry (zero risk from here)             |
//|    TP1     → price at entry ± slDist × 1.0R                     |
